data.description: What a Gem!  Picture yourself enjoying this spacious, open living area with modern finishes like engineered hardwood floors and granite countertops. You’ll love living on this quiet cul-de-sac with your spacious yard looking into the trees behind your home. The freshly stained deck is a perfect spot to enjoy the fall colors or just the serenity of an evening. Almost brand new, this home has been well cared for, and it shows. Be sure to notice the full brick exterior, lots of storage options throughout the home and a fantastic oversized lot. Don’t miss this beautiful home with a great floor plan, just minutes from downtown Siloam Springs. Call today to schedule your private showing!
